椮字的基本解释

椮
（槮）
sēn
〔森椮〕（树木）高耸的样子，如“林箫蔓荆，椮椮柞朴。”
古代的一种捕鱼器具：“椮密鱼虽暖，巢危鹤更阴。”

椮字的汉语字典释义

[①]［sēn］
［《廣韻》所今切，平侵，生。］
［《廣韻》楚簪切，平侵，初。］
“椮1”的繁体字。
树木长貌。
[②]［sǎn］
［《廣韻》桑感切，上感，心。］
“椮2”的繁体字。
(1)积柴水中用作捕鱼之具。
(2)引申为潜藏。

Basic explanation of words
Fall
(槮)
sēn
[Sen 椮] (trees) towering, such as "Lin Xiao Man Jing, 椮椮柞朴."
An ancient fishing gear: "Although the secret fish is warm, the nest is more shaded by the dangerous crane."

Chinese dictionary definition of words
[①] [sēn]
["Guangyun" is cut today, flat invaded, and born. ]
["Guangyun" Chu hairpin cut, flat invasion, early. ]
"椮1" in traditional characters.
The trees look good.
[②]［sǎn］
["Guangyun" has a sense of mulberry, a sense of supremacy, and a heart. ]
"椮2" in traditional characters.
(1) The water used to accumulate firewood is used as a fishing gear.
(2) Extended to latent.
